              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15626064/" class="">逼真的假象或施魅的拟真</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Hesperonis/" class=" " title="HESPERONIS">HESPERONIS</a>
              
